@DEPENDENCIES
internal: styles/tokens | icons/PhosphorIcon | hooks/useStaggeredAnimation
external: remotion (Sequence, interpolate)

@STANDARDS
- Staggered animations use timing.fast or timing.medium
- Color coding: success = green, error = red, warning = yellow
- Czech labels: "Mýtus", "Pravda", "Ano", "Ne", "Dělej", "Nedělej"
- TopTenReveal: index 0 = #10, index 9 = #1
